Subject: Secunia Research: Sun Java JDK/JRE Soundbank
	Resource Name Buffer Overflow

====================================================================== 

                     Secunia Research 31/03/2010

    - Sun Java JDK/JRE Soundbank Resource Name Buffer Overflow -

====================================================================== 
Table of Contents

Affected Software....................................................1
